#########################################################################################
## VIM Most used shortcuts 
#########################################################################################

Shortcuts
===========

Modes
-----
- i                     :   Enter inser mode
- ctrl + v              :   Enter visual mode (selecting will select the chars)
- shift + v             :   Enter visual mode (selecting will select the whole line)

Navigate
--------
- <number>G             :   Goto linenumber: <number>

Deletes
-------
- dd                    :   Delete a whole line
- dw                    :   Delete a word
- d$                    :   Delete until end of line (from cursor)
- <number>d             :   Delete <number> rows from cursor

Copy paste
----------
- yy                    :   Copy a whole line
- p                     :   Paste 
